channel.title: Www.CbScape.org
channel.description:
New server at www.cbscape.org Staff needed (moderators, forum moderators, and global moderators). This server features skilling, top-notch pking, friendly and helpful staff, custom home/donor areas never seen in other servers, and much much more! All skills trainable excluding construction, (EVEN DUNGEONEERING!). CbScape offers fully functional minigames such as barbarian assault, pest control, warriors guild, and even more. 100% custom skilling area; including mining, fishing, smithing etc. click here to play http://cbscape-org.webs.com/
if you dont trust the link, simply type in: www.cbscape.org. SEE YOU ON! :D
